snippet.description:
Subscribe for more GTLive action! ►►http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9 
Mario Maker: BEWARE 7th Grade! ►► http://bit.ly/1NJGoFG
Would You Rather - StankPat Begins! ►► http://bit.ly/1NJGzAO

We partnered with Verizon to set a World Record and showcase some new Minecraft tech. But I can't set the World Record all by myself, so I'm joined by a group of loyal theorists who have come to aid me. Come hangout with all of us and show your support as the Theorists attempt to set a new world record, by creating the World's Largest Minecraft Selfie!

Follow all the updates on new episodes of GTLive!

Subscribe & hang out with us every day! ►►http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9
Follow us on Twitter at @MatPatGT and #GTLive

Don't have much time but need a quick fix? Check out some of our highlight episodes for hilarious moments from our live streams. Here are a few to get you started.

HiLite: Flappy Mario Maker - Just Do IT! ►► http://bit.ly/1OOyOyL
HiLite: Ugliest MII Ever - Wii Sports ►► http://bit.ly/1WUF4Fa
HiLite: Chubby Bunny Sing Off! ►► http://bit.ly/1L3SH1l
